{"tid":2261466,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿報道下架 now主管︰唔想變TVB","createTime":"2020-10-28T10:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:05:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a81a3fb63a3e59f22f7eb553794b6690b45d2abe","tid":2261466,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/LEK2GRNA45FRHH4EKHQUCJT4CU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FLEK2GRNA45FRHH4EKHQUCJT4CU%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7HbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=afd07201\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FLEK2GRNA45FRHH4EKHQUCJT4CU%2F&h=316482a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/LEK2GRNA45FRHH4EKHQUCJT4CU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不滿報道下架 now主管︰唔想變TVB<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UNxMmlHODye_0-qSD6_aK_L8flg=/720x667/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PXCVQOUGANFZLIZVGFDKWM5MSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUNxMmlHODye_0-qSD6_aK_L8flg%3D%2F720x667%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPXCVQOUGANFZLIZVGFDKWM5MSY.jpg&h=e1ee7f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳鐵彪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】now新聞及財經資訊主管陳鐵彪下令將評論候任港大副校長申作軍疑是中共黨員的新聞下架，引起新聞審查的質疑。據悉，now新聞台多名部門主管質疑下架的需要，又認為陳繞過採訪主任直接下令，有做壞規矩之嫌，強調「唔想成為另一個TVB」。陳鐵彪堅持報道有問題，不滿事件在外流傳。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：校委會通過清華幫做副校  港大生研推翻任命<br />\n<br />\n據悉，now新聞台各部門主管及採訪主任昨與陳鐵彪開會討論「葉建源：冀港大澄清申作軍是。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「唔想成為另一個TVB」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳鐵彪死撐「有問題」<br />\n<br />\n陳鐵彪早前回應「眾新聞」時曾指「我認為不適合咪落架囉！」他昨在會議仍堅持報道「有問題」，並對有關消息在社會流傳感不滿，令他成為焦點，惹來抨擊。各部門會上決定，日後對新聞的意見需集體討論，再由採訪主任向下屬下指令，避免有人一錘定音。本報多次致電陳鐵彪未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：柏克萊：申作軍否認黨員<br />\n<br />\n消息人士關注，now日前回應事件的聲明以「now TV」名義發出，而非「now新聞台」，或顯示事件驚動now TV管理層。<br />\n<br />\n陳鐵彪所指報道「有問題」之處仍未釐清，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"5b933f22d9b1978ce1636a7c69802a95fbd29ad3","tid":2261466,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔下架我都冇咁留意呢單野 多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f63a436d5d62662a45cc2a6e343623e7b48486","tid":2261466,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"呢d暗共黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c116031e5eb09542a0ce690650b25101ddc9221a","tid":2261466,"uid":69289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"中央二台（CCNOW news)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bae0bd0a195daefdc54fed954b3cc6486f85075","tid":2261466,"uid":233905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"唔知佢想唔想成為林彬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc74a51798e981ba753866193f4fdcfb8b5cbdcd","tid":2261466,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"呢個四眼龜頭就係陳鐵彪?"},{"pid":"1b48daebb2e887505a7f1c0ec5bff9babe0c83fa","tid":2261466,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"麥兜個校長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}